text.section:
With respect to any referendum conducted under KRS 247.6040 to 247.6070, the Commissioner shall publicly announce through the medium of the public press at least thirty (30) days before the date determined for the referendum, the following information:
The rules and regulations with respect to the holding of the referendum;
The area within which the referendum will be conducted;
The date, hours, and polling places for voting in the referendum;
The effective date of the assessment, if adopted;
The basis of the assessment proposed to be collected;
The means by which the assessment shall be collected if authorized by the growers;
The general purposes to which any amount shall be applied; and
How the proceeds from the assessment shall be administered.
